cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.CL, cs.MM 

This paper is about semantic segmentation, which is a computer vision task. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper proposes a new network architecture for semantic segmentation, which involves designing sub-networks and using deep semantic boundary supervision. This suggests that the paper may also be relevant to the sub-categories of machine learning (cs.LG), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), natural language processing (cs.CL), and multimedia (cs.MM).
